Complete File Listing
---------------------
  config.yaml                              — pipeline parameters and paths
  utils.py                                 — Python utility module (preprocessing)
  utils_correlation.py                     — Python utility module (correlation)
  01_cellranger_count.smk                  — Snakemake: FASTQ → count matrices
  02_cellranger_annotate.smk               — Snakemake: automated annotation
  03_qc_preprocessing_annotation.py       — Python: QC, clustering, annotation
  04_annotation_concordance_AMPPD.py      — Python: cross-dataset correlation
  05_pseudobulk_de_dreamlet.R             — R: pseudobulk DE + fgsea
  06_gsea_clusterProfiler.R               — R: targeted GSEA
  README                                   — this file

Inputs
------
Raw FASTQ files:
  Six samples — Blanchard-wt-snRNAseq-{a,b}, Blanchard-A53T-E3-snRNAseq-{a,b},
  Blanchard-A53T-E4-snRNAseq-{a,b} — are deposited under the dataset DOI
  associated with this manuscript.

Reference datasets used for annotation concordance (step 04):
  - AMP-PD / PPMI postmortem brain snRNA-seq
    (FreshMG freeze 3; T. Clarence et al.)
  - AMPPD_freeze2_7_cx_rareMut pseudobulk aggregations

GMT files (step 05):
  MSigDB v7.5.1 — c2.cp.kegg.v7.5.1.symbols.gmt
                  c5.go.bp.v7.5.1.symbols.gmt
                  c5.go.mf.v7.5.1.symbols.gmt

Key Intermediate Files
----------------------
  2026_New.h5ad                      — concatenated raw AnnData (post Cell Ranger)
  2026_New_Annot1.h5ad               — final annotated AnnData (step 03 output)
  miBRAIN_CLASS_cova_Diff.rds        — dreamlet model fit object (step 05 output)
  miBRAIN_dreamlet_degs_all_clusters.rds — all DEGs (step 05 output)

Final tabular outputs
---------------------
